<!--
       <entry>double if any <replaceable>a</> is double, else integer</>
       <entry>smallest value among arguments</>
-->
       <entry><replaceable>a</>のどれかがdoubleならdouble、そうでなければinteger</>
       <entry>引数の中で最小の値</>
       <entry><literal>least(5, 4, 3, 2.1)</></>
       <entry><literal>2.1</></>
